name: Home
story: You suddenly wake up in your home with a stone in your hand and a revelation in your mind. The reveltion is asking you to find the three other elemental stones in order to prevent the resurrection of the demon king and stop RAGNAROK, the destruction of the world.
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Starter Village Argon and 2 to go to the Village Border..

name: Village
story: You are now in the Starter village Argon. You must prepare yourself for the rough journey ahead of you.
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Village Border and 1 to return to your Home..

name: Border
story: You are now at the border of the village Argon and be prepared once you leave the border there is no turning back.
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Pathway, 2 to go to the Village Argon and 3 to go back Home..

name: Pathway
story: You are currently at the Pathway that leads to the forest. Goodluck!..You will need it.
nav: Enter 1 to go to the forest..

name: Forest
story: You have just entered the Dark Forest where danger waits for you at every turn.
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Hut, 2 to go to the Pond and 3 to go to the Tree house..

name: Hut
story: You find a weird hut in the middle of the forest. Let's explore.
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Pond, 2 to go to the Tree house and 3 to return to the Forest..

name: Pond
story: Seems like there is a pond in the forest, care to go for a dive…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Tree house and 2 to go to the River..

name: Treehouse
story: There is a run down tree house at your sight, If you want you can rest in there..
nav: Enter 1 to go to the River and 2 to return to the Forest…

name: River
story: You are now at an intersection with a river at sight..
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Ship and 2 to return to the Pond..

name: Boat
story: There is a boat in the river ready to set sale you better hurry and catch upto it..
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Water City..

name: Watercity
story: You are now in the city filled with water, Water City..the home of the water spirit Undine…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Inn and 2 to go to the Water temple..

name: Inn
story: You find a small inn in the city…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Water temple…

name: Watertemple
story: You are now at the water temple..You should meet the Priestess in order to get the elemental stone of water..
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Dimensional Portal and 2 to go to the Inn..

name: Portal
story: You have reached a dimensional portal…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the desert, 2 to go the Water temple and 3 to return to the Pathway…

name: Desert
story: You are now in a deep desert and a perilous journey awaits…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Fire city and 2 to return to the Dimensional Portal..

name: Fire City
story: You are now in the nation of fire..Fire Nation..It's the home of the fire spirit Ifrit…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Volcano and 2 to return to the Desert..

name: Volcano
story: You are now in a volcano where you will find the Fire temple…
nav: Enter 1 to go the Fire temple…

name: Fire Temple
story: You are now at the Fire temple..You should meet the Priestess in order to get the elemental stone of Fire..
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Airship…

name: Airship
story: You are now at the Airship ready to set sail to your next location..
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Clouds and 2 to return to the Dimensional Portal…

name: Clouds
story: You are fascinated by the floors made of clouds, Be carefull that you you don't fall of from them..HAHAHAHA…Just Kidding..
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Sky Island…

name: Sky Island
story: You are now in the Island of Wind..Sky Island..It's the home of the Wind spirit Vanitas…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Wind temple…

name: Wind Temple
story: You are now at the Wind temple..You should meet the Priestess in order to get the elemental stone of Wind..
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Air balloon and 2 to go to the Air ship…

name: Air Balloon
story: You are now in the air balloon, It will take you to your next destination…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Elemental Mountain and 2 to go to the Dimensional Portal…

name: Elemental Mountain
story: Welcome to the elemental mountain…
nav: Enter 1 to go to the Dark alter and 2 to go to the Elemental alter…

name: Dark Alter
story: You are currently in front of the dark alter..Place the elemental stones to end your tedious journey..
nav: Enter 1 to conclude your tedious journey…

name: Elemental Alter
story: You are currently in front of the elemental alter..Place the elemental stones to end your tedious journey..
nav: Enter 1 to conclude your tedious journey…

name: Demon King
story: Hahahaha…Idiot..You just wasted your entire effort..The demon king is resurrected and you are the sole reason for that..The elemental stones you found should have been placed in the elemental alter but you choose to place it in the dark alter..and ressurected the demon king..HAHAHAAHA!!!Now as I promised you may end your journey by Dying...

name: Divine Goddess
story: Thank you..Brave hero for stopping the resurrection of the demon king..You have my eternal gratitude..Now you may end your tedious journey with the blessing of the Gods..You will always have a wonderful life ahead…Again Thank you…
